      <outline type="rss" text="Sabin Civil Engineering" title="Sabin Civil Engineering" xmlUrl="https://www.youtube.com/feeds/videos.xml?channel_id=UCqZQJ4600a9wIfMPbYc60OQ" htmlUrl="http://www.youtube.com/feeds/videos.xml?channel_id=UCqZQJ4600a9wIfMPbYc60OQ" description="Sabin Civil Engineering  was founded by Sabin Mathew, an IIT Delhi post graduate in 2012. Here we aim to present various civil engineering topics in a simple way with the help of experiments and clear illustrations. Our videos are designed to clear misconceptions and create a passion for engineering." language="en_US" />
      <outline type="rss" text="Silicon Valley Girl" title="Silicon Valley Girl" xmlUrl="https://www.youtube.com/feeds/videos.xml?channel_id=UCiq1FIgtEK7LRAOB1JXTPig" htmlUrl="http://www.youtube.com/feeds/videos.xml?channel_id=UCiq1FIgtEK7LRAOB1JXTPig" description="Positive about tech and how it can improve our lives. Passionate about building and creating. Immigrant, mom, entrepreneur." language="en_US" />
      <outline type="rss" text="StatQuest with Josh Starmer" title="StatQuest with Josh Starmer" xmlUrl="https://www.youtube.com/feeds/videos.xml?channel_id=UCtYLUTtgS3k1Fg4y5tAhLbw" htmlUrl="http://www.youtube.com/feeds/videos.xml?channel_id=UCtYLUTtgS3k1Fg4y5tAhLbw" description="Statistics, Machine Learning, Data Science, and AI seem like very scary topics, but since each technique is really just a combination of small and simple steps, they are actually quite simple. My goal with StatQuest is to break down the major methodologies into easy-to-understand pieces. That said, I don&apos;t dumb down the material. Instead, I build up your understanding so that you are smarter." language="en_US" />
